headline.main: Pelicans Beat Lakers 105-97 for 1st Win With Cousins in Game
headline.print_headline: Pelicans Beat Lakers 105-97 for 1st Win With Cousins in Game

lead_paragraph: Five games into his trade to the Pelicans, DeMarcus Cousins wanted something to show for it. Like a win.
